"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president wants China to open up more, while China is expected to ask about Taiwan. Trump has arrived in Beijing for the first time since 2017.\",            \"english_title\": \"US President Visits China\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de EE.UU. quiere que China se abra m\u00e1s, mientras que se espera que China pregunte sobre Taiw\u00e1n. Trump ha llegado a Pek\u00edn por primera vez desde 2017.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Presidente de EE.UU. visita China\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A court has ordered a new trial for the June 2021 killings of Paul and Maggie Murdaugh.\",            \"english_title\": \"New Trial Ordered\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un tribunal ha ordenado un nuevo juicio por los asesinatos de Paul y Maggie Murdaugh en junio de 2021.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Nuevo juicio ordenado\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Police commandos entered a building where a senator wanted by the International Criminal Court was hiding.\",            \"english_title\": \"Senator Hiding\",            \"translated_version\": \"Comandos de polic\u00eda entraron en un edificio donde se escond\u00eda un senador buscado por la Corte Penal Internacional.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Senador escondido\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Two children are among those reported dead after seven cars were hit in separate attacks south of Beirut.\",            \"english_title\": \"Children Among Dead\",            \"translated_version\": \"Dos ni\u00f1os est\u00e1n entre los muertos despu\u00e9s de que siete coches fueran atacados en ataques separados al sur de Beirut.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ni\u00f1os entre los muertos\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Six people have been killed after Zelensky warned of more Russian strikes through Wedne